episodes.title: Cults & Coaching
episodes.description: Let's talk about cults, baby. Yep we are going there. Twin Flames. Teal Swan. One Taste. Why is personal development and spiritual healing such a common target for cult leaders? What are the commons signs of a culty space? And, what is my personal experience being in a culty space? How can you make sure you are not in one or creating one? Let's talk about it. Tag me on Instagram @emilyannebrant and share this episode if it was helpful or valuable in any way. Join my free Facebook community Let's Decolonize Coaching.
